4308  /*!
4309  * \brief Interpolate variables to a coarser grid level.
4310  * \note Halo values are not communicated in this function.
4311  * \param[in] geoFine - Fine grid.
4312  * \param[in] varsFine - Matrix of variables on the fine grid.
4313  * \param[in] geoCoarse - Coarse grid.
4314  * \param[in] varsCoarse - Matrix of variables interpolated to the coarse grid.
4315  */
4316  inline static void MultigridRestriction(const CGeometry& geoFine, const su2activematrix& varsFine,
4317  const CGeometry& geoCoarse, su2activematrix& varsCoarse) {
4318  SU2_OMP_FOR_STAT(roundUpDiv(geoCoarse.GetnPointDomain(), omp_get_num_threads()))
4319  for (auto iPointCoarse = 0ul; iPointCoarse < geoCoarse.GetnPointDomain(); ++iPointCoarse) {
4320 
4321  for (auto iVar = 0ul; iVar < varsCoarse.cols(); iVar++) {
4322  varsCoarse(iPointCoarse, iVar) = 0.0;
4323  }
4324  const su2double scale = 1 / geoCoarse.nodes->GetVolume(iPointCoarse);
4325 
4326  for (auto iChildren = 0ul; iChildren < geoCoarse.nodes->GetnChildren_CV(iPointCoarse); ++iChildren) {
4327  const auto iPointFine = geoCoarse.nodes->GetChildren_CV(iPointCoarse, iChildren);
4328  const su2double w = geoFine.nodes->GetVolume(iPointFine) * scale;
4329  for (auto iVar = 0ul; iVar < varsCoarse.cols(); ++iVar) {
4330  varsCoarse(iPointCoarse, iVar) += w * varsFine(iPointFine, iVar);
4331  }
4332  }
4333  }
4334  END_SU2_OMP_FOR
4335  }

4348  /*!
4349  * \brief "Add" residual at (iPoint,iVar) to residual variables local to the thread.
4350  * \param[in] iPoint - Point index.
4351  * \param[in] iVar - Variable index.
4352  * \param[in] res - Residual at (iPoint,iVar), e.g. LinSysRes(iPoint,iVar)
4353  * \param[in,out] resRMS - increases by pow(Residual, 2)
4354  * \param[in,out] resMax - increases to max(resMax, Residual)
4355  * \param[in,out] idxMax - changes when resMax increases
4356  */
4357  static inline void ResidualReductions_PerThread(unsigned long iPoint, unsigned short iVar, su2double res, su2double* resRMS, su2double* resMax,
4358  unsigned long* idxMax) {
4359  res = fabs(res);
4360  resRMS[iVar] += res * res;
4361  if (res > resMax[iVar]) {
4362  resMax[iVar] = res;
4363  idxMax[iVar] = iPoint;
4364  }
4365  }
4366 
4367  /*!
4368  * \brief "Add" local residual variables of all threads to compute global residual variables.
4369  */
4370  inline void ResidualReductions_FromAllThreads(const CGeometry* geometry, const CConfig* config, const su2double* resRMS, const su2double* resMax,
4371  const unsigned long* idxMax){
4372  SetResToZero();
4373 
4374  SU2_OMP_CRITICAL
4375  for (unsigned short iVar = 0; iVar < nVar; iVar++) {
4376  Residual_RMS[iVar] += resRMS[iVar];
4377  AddRes_Max(iVar, resMax[iVar], geometry->nodes->GetGlobalIndex(idxMax[iVar]), geometry->nodes->GetCoord(idxMax[iVar]));
4378  }
4379  END_SU2_OMP_CRITICAL
4380  SU2_OMP_BARRIER
4381 
4382  /*--- Compute the root mean square residual ---*/
4383  SetResidual_RMS(geometry, config);
4384  }
4385 
4386  /*!
4387  * \brief Set the RMS and MAX residual to zero.
4388  */
4389  inline void SetResToZero() {
4390  BEGIN_SU2_OMP_SAFE_GLOBAL_ACCESS {
4391  for (auto& r : Residual_RMS) r = 0;
4392  for (auto& r : Residual_Max) r = 0;
4393  for (auto& p : Point_Max) p = 0;
4394  }
4395  END_SU2_OMP_SAFE_GLOBAL_ACCESS
4396  }
